    "33cd68d7-40f1-47b2-a68f-7d44f0b98908": {
      "type": "section-richtext",
      "settings": {
        "kicker": "",
        "title": "",
        "text": "<h1>Salon Aftercare</h1><p>At HairMNL, we're passionate about hair care, and it's not just about selling products – it's about helping you maintain the beauty of your hair. Our Salon Aftercare Collections are carefully curated to address the specific needs of different hair treatments, ensuring your locks remain healthy, vibrant, and full of life.</p><ul><li><strong>Expertly Formulated:</strong> Our products are designed by experts in the field to enhance and prolong the effects of salon treatments.</li><li><strong>Tailored to Your Needs:</strong> Whether you have color-treated hair, rebonded locks, permed waves, a Brazilian blowout, keratin-treated strands, or bleached beauty, we have the right aftercare products to meet your unique needs.</li><li><strong>Radiant Results:</strong> With our aftercare collections, you can expect long-lasting color, smoothness, definition, frizz control, and vibrant blonde locks.</li><li><strong>Professional Quality at Home: </strong>Enjoy salon-quality care from the comfort of your own home.</li><li><strong>Healthy Hair, Always:</strong> Our products are formulated to keep your hair healthy and strong, so you can continue to flaunt the stunning results of your salon treatment.</li></ul><p>Explore our Salon Aftercare Collections and indulge your hair in the pampering it deserves. Discover the difference in maintaining the beauty of your hair with HairMNL.</p>",
        "text_size": 2,
        "text_columns": 1,
        "align_text": "text-left",
